title: Ronnie Dunn Reveals Which Song He Would Eliminate From A Brooks & Dunn Set List + Morgan2 And Mike D Are Going On A Double Date + Bobby Has A New Voice In His Head
itunes:title: Ronnie Dunn Reveals Which Song He Would Eliminate From A Brooks & Dunn Set List + Morgan2 And Mike D Are Going On A Double Date + Bobby Has A New Voice In His Head
description:
Ronnie Dunn stops by the studio for the Friday Morning Conversation. We talk to him about his new album of cover songs, what song he’d take out of a Brooks and Dunn set list and if he’s ever made a big bet while in Vegas. 'PHD Peter' calls in and Morgan2 agrees to go on a double date with him and Mike D and his girlfriend. It turns out Bobby names the voices in his head…his latest one is making him want to eat sugar.
